message.body: Hey so I was thinking about organizing the ideas/events lists we have on the google doc for discussion at the first meeting.. But then realized that might be Ilana's job? What do you think?
Secretary....it could be hers or yours....could fall under either. I actually have a list of things we need to discuss =P
Hahaha or if you already have a list that should be good! Just want to keep everything organized
Of course! Lemme send it to you, tell me if you need anything
Maybe it'll be good to send it to everyone to have them think it all over beforehand and include anything we misses
Missed*
Good call! Will do tomorrow
Were you able to book the teaching lab? And should we look into getting food lol
I'm going into city tomorrow. Kiran never answered my email so I'm just gonna go in, haha. AND YES FOOD
Haha good idea. Or maybe conference room if its available cause I know we can eat there
Yes yes! I'll see for sure tomorrow. Once it's confirmed, email goes out
Awesome let me know if you need any help!
Actually, you know all the good food places....would you like to order? LOLZ
Haha ill ask people what they're in the mood for!
Thank you! You are a saint
Haha no I just love food
And you're good at it =P
Were you able to contact your roommates?
Ugh. I emailed them on Thursday and still no response
Ahh awkward haha
That's weird though! I'm sure they'd wanna talk
Right!? Ugh, people. Haha
It's ok I'm pretty sure I emailed one of my suite mates during the summer more than we actually spoke last semester
LOLOL. Are you gonna go off campus for senior year?
Nah I'm staying in Broome haha
You can guarantee that!?
Hmm idk I know before w res college you were able to stay but since its different now idk didn't think about that
Ahh, I gotcha. Hopefully you can! Broome looks nice
Yeah I'm not to worried I'm sure they don't kick out people who were originally part of res college
Ahh just realized I can finally see my new suite mate haha time to stalk
Ummmmm by any chance is Ross a girls name?
.........I mean.....maybe it's short for Roseanne....!?
Wait nvm it says female
But that's weird hahaha
That is weird, hahaha
I bet you 5 bucks your suite mate talks to you before mine....
Hahaha aw don't worry I've honestly never been friends with any roommate or suitemate and I like it that way
I am perfectly fine with that. I just want to get in contact with them, so I know if I need to bring anything =P
Ah found her we have mutual friends and in her cover photo she's in the Philippines haha
Approval! She is a real person!
Her middle name is Ross haha or at least on her FB it is. This might be good haha
Haha. Okay, so she's a girl confirmed! Weird middle name....
I always hope I can make a friend out of a suitemate haha but we'll see
Haha. It's sometimes dangerous. I was good friends with everyone in my room last year, but my one friend went psycho....
Oh gosh what happened??

She (Alexa) and her roommate Hallie were on and off best friends/sworn enemies. Hallie and I decided it'd be best for us to room together, and Alexa had plans to room with our friend Ellen....but then Alexa decided that NO, she wanted Hallie that day and made my life hell
I later found out that Hallie told Alexa that I was opposed to her atheism, to get out of rooming with her. (None of this was true ever). So yeah...0
Wtf haha that's so weird
Oh freshman year
Haha well it's only a semester and I feel like upperclassmen dorming is a lot less drama
Hence why I'm terrified of what's happening with roommates =P
Haha, fair enough. I sure hope so! Thanks
Were you able to figure out who they were at least?
Yeah yeah. Their names and emails finally showed up. My friend Dan is apparently good at stalking and found them all on LinkedIn
Oo good sign if they have LinkedIn! Professional haha
Professional folks! (I felt so freaking creepy)
It's ok it encouraged me to look at my suitemates haha
It's good to have an idea of what's coming!
Haha, definitely! I need to make an account....or at least update it
Eh I've found it pretty useless haha
Haha, fair enough. WAIT let me send you the list

NSSLHA Meeting 2/4 -Introductions -Blackboard gone, so use NSSLHA gmail (Ilana's biweekly email!) and try to save things for meetings -No big projects w/o consulting; consolidate FB (Lauren) -Events (plan AND satisfaction) -T shirts -go over NSSLHA constitution (if time)
How to bring awareness!
YES!
I think a consolidated Facebook page would definitely help our case
I don't know how to do it though! Like we can't delete the one in the NYU group I don't think
Wait. There's a CSD one, an NYU NSSLHA one, and is there a different one with NYU?
If we can't delete one, lets at least make only one of them active
There's 3 lol
Well see the CSD one is about the major and not the club
Ah, true. Where the hell is the second NSSLHA one?!
It's not NSSLHA it's for the department lol search NYU steinhardt undergraduate - communicative sciences & disorders
There's 2 CSDs and 1 NSSLHA then?
Can we kill one CSD?
Yeah I think the one with steinhardt in the name is pretty much dead
As Social Media Chair, we'll have Lauren kill it
Haha sounds good
Got the reservation for the teaching lab!
Awesome!
Hey we should finalize the interview questions and what role everyone will have in the process
We already have one with questions so maybe we can organize that?
I can do it right now
Ooh. Very very good idea - should we start up a document?
Sounds good to me - the questions look great! Does it matter who asks what question...?
No but I think it would be good for us to each ask one so its not so intimidating lol
Hahaha. That's fair. I'm watching you edit this now, SO COOL
I'll alert everyone to the document and tell everyone to take a question or two
Ok sounds good! Or we can just wing it when we get there lol we don't need to assign specific questions
Haha, fair. I'll still alert everyone to it so they can check it out and add if they feel it's necessary
Yup! And we can always ask additional questions during the interview as well
Also will we all be taking notes? Or just Ilana
Of course! Gina says for USG rep, we REALLY need to stress being at the USG meetings
Ilana definitely has to. I personally want to take notes, because the things that strike me might be different than those that strike Ilana, etc.....it's personal choice =P
I wonder what happened to Ali
How did you contact her? Any sign of FB usage or anything haha
Ok I just don't want everyone to be looking at a notebook the whole time or whatever lol
I gotcha, haha. I'll be doing shorthand stuff, but I don't think everyone has to take notes
Yeah and with the extra time left we can do like a review thing before we vote haha
Email and Facebook, it says she saw the Facebook message! And definitely yes. A discussion couldn't hurt, although we don't want to influence each other too much. Haha
Of course but just to remind each
Other what we heard! So she saw your message but didn't reply?
I think so - I'll have to check again, but I swear it says "Seen by Ali and 2 others"
Hmm I wonder if we should try to contact her again
That's probably a really good idea
Try emailing this time? And after that don't bother contacting
Definitely going to. If she doesn't answer, makes our job easier
Maybe she doesn't want to follow through with it
It's worth asking! I'll send her an email when I get in
Ok sounds good!
Emailed Ali, I give her until tomorrow before I send the applicants their finalized schedule. Anything I should tell them before the interview?
Hm can't think of anything!
Hahaha
"come with any questions or concerns. Happy Hunger Games, and may the odds be ever in your favor"
Wait if Ali doesn't do it anymore do we still interview grace and mike?
Yeah definitely I wanna meet them!
If Ali officially backs out, we tell them they've got it - but they're more than welcome to come in and chat. Once I get a response from Ali, I'll invite Melissa to come in if she's ae
*able. It might be good for them all to get a feel for us anyway
Me too!! Grace was in my group for the scavenger hunt, and I already love her. Met Melissa, she's a doll
And apparently Mike went to Bishop Ahr (where everyone from my elementary school went)....I gotta ask about him
Really??? Where is he from?
Actually I remember talking to him about this at the scavenger hunt haha. Too young for any mutual friends :(
Apparently Iselin, which is a part of Woodbridge (where my sister lives now!!!)
Haha it's fine remember we don't want to be bias! Although male from central jersey is already working for me hahaha
Haha, awww. Apparently he's too young for me too! Cause none of my Bishop Ahr friends seem to know him =(
Haha, I'm not letting there be any bias!!
Tweeting this lol
.....but he is a man....
HAHAHA YES <3
Next step is to recruit the other guy
We can pretend like we have guys in our major...
We have 3!! It's a big deal haha
It is!! And we need to utilize them ALL
ALL THE MEN
I really think we could entice men to join our major with different marketing and advertising
Like, if we dressed up all cute for the ads and sent them to prospective CSD men
And said "YOU WILL LITERALLY BE SWIMMING IN CHICKS"
Hahaha aw but at the same time I love the feminine feel of it all
Haha. Works very well for us! And the men in our program are just so nice
Very true! But that probably applies for anyone in our program haha
Touché. I feel like you almost HAVE to be absurdly nice to be an SLP
We never have to deal with selfish people!
I love it so much!
One of my good friends is in business and she always complains about rude or selfish people.. Not a problem for us :)
Haha, we are so very lucky =)
Is the Parkinson's Walk we were gonna do the same thing as the Parkinson's Unity Walk? April 29?
No clue but if its the same date then probably haha
Does Hugo know the date? LOLZ
Idk I put a link to it I think on the google doc or just google search it it shouldn't be hard to find
I'm almost positive that's the one =p
Ah! You're so good at organizing stuff, document looks great. =) And Ali's coming in at 6:15!
Haha thanks! And yay awesome :)
I was going through DVDs to bring to school....apparently I own The King's Speech, so movie night is a go whenever
Yay!! Lets do that while its still cold out haha
Haha, that can be one of our first events. It's super easy to plan
Welcome back movie thing?
I love it!
Awesome lets discuss Monday
